collectors.title: Database
collectors.titleDetails: (3 total Queries, 3 of them unique across 1 Connection)

queries.sql: SELECT `mp`.`nama_pendapatan`, SUM(dp.jumlah) as total FROM `detail_pendapatan` as `dp` JOIN `master_pendapatan` as `mp` ON `mp`.`id` = `dp`.`master_pendapatan_id` JOIN `bku_bulanan` as `bb` ON `bb`.`id` = `dp`.`bku_id` WHERE STR_TO_DATE(CONCAT(bb.tahun, '-', bb.bulan, '-01'), '%Y-%m-%d') >= '2024-08-29' AND STR_TO_DATE(CONCAT(bb.tahun, '-', bb.bulan, '-01'), '%Y-%m-%d') <= '2025-08-29' GROUP BY `mp`.`nama_pendapatan`

SELECT `mkp`.`nama_kategori`, SUM(dp.jumlah) as total FROM `detail_pengeluaran` as `dp` JOIN `master_kategori_pengeluaran` as `mkp` ON `mkp`.`id` = `dp`.`master_kategori_id` JOIN `bku_bulanan` as `bb` ON `bb`.`id` = `dp`.`bku_id` WHERE STR_TO_DATE(CONCAT(bb.tahun, '-', bb.bulan, '-01'), '%Y-%m-%d') >= '2024-08-29' AND STR_TO_DATE(CONCAT(bb.tahun, '-', bb.bulan, '-01'), '%Y-%m-%d') <= '2025-08-29' GROUP BY `mkp`.`nama_kategori`
